 -------------
   FEATURES:
 -------------
  *  Compatible with all Amiga range computers (including AGA machines).

  *  Built-in game designer for designing your own levels.

  *  High playability and attractive game design.

  *  Single part game file (not requires any data files or libraries).

  *  Easy harddrive installation (simply drag its icon to anywhere).

 --------------
   GAME KEYS:
 --------------
  *  'P' ..... Pause

  *  'ESC' ... Quit


